{"tid":240844,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"大塜愛結婚7年 老公被爆偷食𡃁模","createTime":"2017-05-12T17:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-13T13:45:55.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3d241bd06222dd4c0cff60e5ed1cd5cc33f37c4a","tid":240844,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T17:18:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/04/07/phpsymDXI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F04%2F07%2FphpsymDXI.jpg&h=2ca710f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大塜愛7年前奉子成婚，婚後爭吵不斷。（翻攝自網路）<br />\n<br />\n〔娛樂頻道／綜合報導〕日本人氣女歌手大塜愛慘遭老公背叛，最新一期的八卦雜誌拍到她的老公、屎爛幫成員SU，偷吃嫩模江夏詩織，先以邀請特別來賓上節目的名義，與女方一起出現在電台，接著兩人在一起離開，然後回到對方的香閨！<br />\n<br />\n大塜愛7年前奉子成婚，兩人婚後爭吵不斷，如今老公被八卦雜誌逮個正著，但兩人都還沒有回應，也不知道這段婚姻還走不走得下去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/04/07/php7Pzpez.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F04%2F07%2Fphp7Pzpez.jpg&h=e6e28ab4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n江夏詩織傳出不倫戀。（翻攝自網路）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/04/07/phpAzNm3u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F04%2F07%2FphpAzNm3u.jpg&h=9c7e02e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSU（右）被拍到與江夏詩織（左）一起離開電台，直奔女方的香閨。（翻攝自網路）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2028784\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2028784&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eZ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=d0554cc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2028784&h=226d476f\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2028784</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c277a14df19422f9ec0516223151d99bdeb61000